riod and of the exponential factor\nwould allow to determine Delta, independently.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2002 13:25:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Oct 2002 21:39:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
